title: 09/29/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, Patriots Insider Tom E. Curran joins the show to discuss Tom Brady's visit to Foxboro this weekend. Does he expect TB12 and Belichick to exchange pleasantries. Fresh off his team's blow out of Wisconsin, Notre Dame Head Coach Brian Kelly calls in to talk about being the all-time winningest Coach at Notre Dame. And Dan discusses whether he thinks the clock is ticking on Big Ben.
